      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>Wait, I think you got the candidates mixed up. I'm working for Vance, so the critique should be against her *opponent*. The plan I'm talking about is the one proposed by the opponent, not Vance's. Can you rewrite it so it's a direct attack on the opponent's plan? Make it even more aggressive—really frame them as being out of touch and dangerous for the economy.",
